articles.title: Celebrities and stars react to actor-rapper DMX's sudden death at 50 years old - CNA
articles.description: NEW YORK (Reuters) -American rapper and actor Earl Simmons, known by the stage name DMX or Dark Man X, died on Friday (April 9), his record label said, after he suffered a heart attack during what media reports said was a drug overdose. He was 50 years old.
